tracks.title: Jean-Michel Jarre & Tangerine Dream - Zero Gravity (Above & Beyond Remix)
tracks.description:
"For me, Jean-Michel Jarre is one of the founding fathers of electronic music. His music has always been sonically and musically creative, so when I first heard his music as kid it was one of the main things that inspired me to want to make electronic music. Jarre also created the big show format for an electronic performer. 

I recall first discovering Tangerine Dream via the soundtrack to "Risky Business" and was very sad to hear of Edgar Froese's recent passing. 

It was an honour to work with these two legends of electronica on our remix of “Zero Gravity" - the idea was to draw on the early influences from their music combined with ideas from the track itself, and then inject some Above & Beyond into the mix."

Jono - Above & Beyond

tracks.title: Michael Franks - Lotus Blossom (Metasine Remix)
tracks.description:
With summer & festival season getting into full swing, WUMP wanted to give you all a little treat to enhance that warm, summer night bliss in the form of a saxy, sensual tune by Metasine.  With this release, we would also like to announce that Metasine has put the finishing touches on his upcoming "Still Dreaming" extended play collection, and we will be releasing that 6-track masterpiece this summer. 

Metasine revived this classic Michael Franks song with a groovy, simple beat that progresses with the addition of his own saxophone, groovy synths, and even some wub-wubs.  This will be your go-to summer, feel-good song, with its catchy vocals and creative layering that will inevitably have you singing along with a smile on your face.  

As a reward to you all for showing so much love and support on our very young journey thus far, we are giving this one up as a free download!  Grab your free copy, share it with your friends, and enjoy the summertime vibes.
